---
title: Seed-Crusted Chicken with Bulgur Salad
description: Chewy, earthy bulgur is the perfect vessel for savoury, super seed-crusted chicken tenders. This salad is packed full of goodness: cucumbers, tomatoes, spring mix and feta!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-en-croute-de-graines-f9a1fbc8.jpg
